==English==
===Intransitive verb===
'''[[drag]] one’s [[feet]]'''
#{{idiom}} To [[procrastinate]], [[put off]]; to [[dawdle]], [[avoid]], or make progress slowly and [[reluctant]]ly.
#:''I have been '''dragging my feet''' about filing my taxes.''

